@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/fee-reminders

### Student: My Fee Reminders
GET {{baseUrl}}/student/{{STUDENT_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{STUDENT_TOKEN}}

### Admin/Warden: All Fee Reminders
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/all
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}

### Admin/Warden: Stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}

### Admin/Warden: Update Status
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/{{FEE_REMINDER_ID}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Paid"
}

### Admin: Create Fee Reminder
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/create
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "{{STUDENT_ID}}",
  "amount": 5000,
  "dueDate": "2025-02-01"
}

### Admin: Create Fee Reminders For All Students
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/create-all
Authorization: Bearer {{ADMIN_TOKEN}}


